    <item>
      <title>拜登政府将发布规则堵住枪展漏洞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/biden-administration-to-issue-rule-closing-gun-show-loophole</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府正在颁布一项规则，旨在缩小允许枪支购买者避免背景调查的差距，官员们称这是几十年来打击无证经销商的最重要步骤之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/biden-administration-to-issue-rule-closing-gun-show-loophole</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 09:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国加强与日本、菲律宾的关系以在海上对抗中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/to-counter-china-in-south-china-sea-us-ramps-up-ties-with-japan-philippines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登将宣布与菲律宾和日本进行联合军事巡逻和训练，这两个盟国寻求对抗在南海日益强势的中国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/to-counter-china-in-south-china-sea-us-ramps-up-ties-with-japan-philippines</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
