      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/lufthansa-suspends-services-to-iran-amid-rising-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东紧张局势升级，德国汉莎航空公司暂停了飞往德黑兰的航班。]]></description>
